In addition to generic characters. Body length: size medium for the genus. Head (
Fig. 2F
): as broad or slightly broader than the thorax; fastigium frontis distinctly wider than scapus; face maximal width (in frontal view, below the eyes) 3.8 times (min: 3.5; max: 4.1; 
holotype
